summary: 1966  was a common year starting on Saturday of the Gregorian calendar.
full_text: 1966  was a common year starting on Saturday  of the Gregorian calendar, the 1966th year of the Common Era  and Anno Domini  designations, the 966th year of the 2nd millennium, the 66th year of the 20th century, and the 7th year of the 1960s decade.
